# Tauri Desktop App Rules

- React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- Dark theme with purple accent (#7c6af7)
- CSS variables defined in `web/src/index.css`
- All select/input elements must use themed styling (hover:border-accent, focus ring, etc.)
- Components in `web/src/components/`; pages in `web/src/pages/`
- State management via Zustand stores in `web/src/stores/`
- API client in `web/src/api/`
- Use lucide-react for icons
- Font: Inter (sans), JetBrains Mono (mono)
- Mobile-responsive with breakpoints at 768px and 1200px
